dataIdInfo.idPurp: Pakistan Provincial Constituency Boundaries Spatial Database prepared by ALHASAN SYSTEMS Private Limited.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: Pakistan Provincial Constituency Boundaries which are prepared by ALHASAN SYSTEMS as free service. These Provincial Constituency Boundaries can be used in Election Mapping and GIS analysis. This is the most up-to-date spatial layer available now in public. ALHASAN SYSTEMS has developed such layers for other areas of Pakistan and will be made available on both www.geopakistan.pkand on Humanitarian Data Exchange portal [https://data.hdx.rwlabs.org/].

Consts.useLimit: There are no access and use limitations for this item.
